\pard\intbl\ql
{The aim of the course is to analyze accounting information from managerial 
purposes and to focus on the quantification of costs and expenses\'2e 
\'46urthermore there is dealt with budgeting issues and investment 
planning\'2e }\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{\~}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
