}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{Upon successful completion of this course, students will be able to: 
\line
\_ explain the differences in substance and management accounting 
system design for product costing and compare it with the accounting 
information for incentives of managers at different levels of management; 
\line
\_ provide breakeven analysis and cost \_ volume analysis\line
\_ select the appropriate structure of product costs and benefits 
depending on decision\_making tasks; \line
\_ select appropriate methods for investment planning analysis under 
conditions of risk and uncertainty\'2e \line
}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{\~}\cell\row\pard
